          "snippet": " You can read more about our cookies before you choose.\n\nYou can change your cookie settings at any time using our cookies page.\n\nMenuClose menu\n\nFurther information on innovator support\n\nGet personalised support\n\nThe key stages from creation to adoption\n\nFind potential funding opportunities\n\nFind out what innovations the NHS is looking for\n\nRead the latest news, case studies and funding opportunities for healthcare innovators. Understand the key stages to bring your product or idea to the NHS and access tailored support through the NHS Innovation Service.\n\nSupporting healthcare innovators\n\nDiscover the key steps you’ll need to take to introduce your idea or product to the NHS. Industry experts, government bodies, the NHS and patient groups have collaborated to provide in-depth information on everything from creation to commissioning and adoption.",
